data.description: Your Dream Home Awaits You! This Custom Built New Construction Home sits on 4+ Acres. This stunning 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home spans nearly 2,700 sqft featuring uniquely designed ceilings and premium marble styled flooring. The open concept floor plan is complimented by an enormous island that sits 6 people. Split bedroom floor plan, spacious master with a huge luxurious closet. Automated lighting, surround sound, security system, Nest thermostats, and much more! 2 car garage slab is poured and ready to be completed. Take advantage of the rare benefits of modern life living with acreage to enjoy. The possibilities are endless for you and your family!
